                  <note/>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>
              <msItem>
                <locus to="" from=""/>
                <title ref="" xml:lang="en">For monks and lay persons</title>
                <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܛܟܣܐ ܕܠܘܘܝܐ ܕܡܫܬܡܠܐ ܥܠ ܕܝܪ̈ܝܐ ܟܫܝܪ̈ܐ. ܘܥܠ ܐܚ̈ܐ ܒ̈ܢܝ ܩܝܡܐ̇ ܘܥܠ
                  ܟܠܢܫ ܕܥܠ ܐܚ̈ܐ.</rubric>
                <note>Each of these services likewise comprises several madrāshē and sūgyāthā,
                  mostly ascribed to Ephraim, foll. 33 a, etc., 42 a etc., and 47 b, etc., but also
                  to Isaac of Antioch, fol. 37 b and Jacob of Batnae, fol. 52 b.</note>
